{
  "stem": "3638.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were still surrounded by the, by the Lithuanian guards, which they change every so often, from Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they had no right, ever, to come interfere with us in, in the factory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They couldn't come in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was arranged through, through Schindler.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Schindler makes that arrangement.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we knew it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't, he did not allow anybody to interfere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The same was in Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He did not let interfere with any of [INAUDIBLE] in his factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were-- the German used to come to make, sometime, inspection from Plaszow, which is the hierarchy of Germans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like they were, [INAUDIBLE] maybe, officer, everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he used to take them upstairs to make, to make them drunk before they went down.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He used to offer some cognac and everything, so that they went back and they say, everything is OK.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were protected.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't work under the German guards.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were not-- we had no contact with the German guards.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nothing at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That, I don't-- that, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's, he's-- I couldn't pick his brain, but I know one thing, that he did not employ any more Polish workers, which he had to pay them, and he employed the Jews.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as the factory grew, he took more Jews from, from Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what I remember, because sometimes used to come new people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as far-- I don't think it was benevolent, because he made money out of it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was purely commercial, at that start.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Purely commercial.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't-- he got paid for us, but he didn't give us any money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He just feed us, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Feed us, and he kept us in comfort.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I should say that he did-- that he was entitled to that.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
